RTCIceCandidatePairStatsLastPacketSentTi.summary: The lastPacketSentTimestamp property of the dictionary indicates the time at which the connection described by the candidate pair last sent a packet, not including {{Glossary("STUN")}} packets.
RTCIceCandidatePairStatsLastPacketSentTi.value: A object indicating the timestamp at which the connection described by pair of candidates last sent a packet, STUN packets excluded.
